One Lake, Macho Flavoured.

A chocolate muffin please.

{Hold your breath
Make a wish
Count to three}

Come with me and you'll be
On a page of pure imagination
Take a look and you'll see
Into your imagination

We'll begin with a spin
Traveling in the world
Of my creation
What we'll see
Will defy explanation

If you want to view a new page
Simply look around and view it
Anything you want to, do it
Wanna change the page?
There's nothing to it

There is no page I know
To compare with
Pure imagination
Living there, you'll be free
If you truly wish to be

If you want to view a new page
Simply look around and view it
Anything you want to, do it
Wanna change the page?
There's nothing to it

There is no life I know
To compare with
Pure imagination
Living there, you'll be free
If you truly wish to be

Edited February 16, 2022 by ColdJ

Here, a new [different] Page for you.

A Saturn V please.

Edited February 16, 2022 by Venusian Explorer

One sat on pea. @Venusian Explorer (please look above your last post.)

One savory crepe and some strawberry ice cream please.

Werner, we've got some creep out here who wants straw!

I'll have the Cobb salad, please.

Jeb's ribs from space, instead.

I want some Minmus ice cream, please.

You get Radioactive materials, Maybe you should ask AtomicTech to build a Radioactive Container.

I want some British Fries.

Water, instead.

I want an emoji cake.

Here is some radioactive yellow cake.

A glass of lemonade. Please.

A glass of Jeb's juice, frozen 3 days. And it's apple juice.

I want some mocha cake, please!

One moccasin. (Sorry but we were all out of cakes that mock you.)

A steak sandwich please.

Here, a Stick Sandwich.

I would like a bunch of Spaghetti.

Sure, a big plate of spaghetti squash!

I'd like a glass of water, no ice...

Ice instead. Chew it, you get water!

I want some lasagna, please.

One laser guided Nana.

I would like a hot pot please.

A pot, heated up to boiling point, or more.

I would like to order a truffle with truffle with truffle seasoning

Here you are.A traffic jam.

I want a Nuclear warhead.

Here is our best of the worst dish of the lifetime: emotional damage.

I want some chocolate cake, please.

Because the cake is a lie, so I lied to you. 

I wish I can have some Plutonium.

You suddenly go to Pluto and you're stranded there forever. Just wait 'till The Destroyer sends his Christmas tree again.

I want some ice cream, vanilla flavored.

The ice cream was so cold that when you touched it, you are killed by it's low temperature. 

I want Jeb.

Jeb attacks you back.

I want Venus rocks.

Venus rocks was made of acid. 

I want a cake.

YOU ARE A LIE GET OUT OF THE RESTAURANT BEFORE WE SUE YOU!

I will order a lemon tea.

The lemon was made of acid. 

I want some neurontoxin.

Muriatic acid in a glass.

I want some noodles, please!
